data.description: Light and bright 2 bedroom 2 bath home on a fully fenced lot near river, Rotary Park, and shopping! This home offers 1,152 sq ft of living space with a bonus room that could be a 3rd bedroom, and full RV hookups including water, power and sewer! Important features include: *Landscaped front and back yards *Covered carport for parking *Large covered patio *Newer vinyl plank flooring *Open floor plan Ceiling fans *Vaulted ceiling *Casual dining *Breakfast bar *Master suite with single vanity, tiled backsplash and walk in shower *Guest bedroom with full guest bath *Indoor laundry with stackable washer and dryer *Large backyard with room for toys!
